    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is the ultimate blank canvas for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and put in some sweat equity. While it currently needs a fair amount of mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a car with great potential at a budget-friendly price. If you love a good restoration challenge, this is the perfect project to make your own!",
